   "source": [
    "# Audit RAG System — Step 1: Environment Setup & Data Ingestion\n",
    "\n",
    "**Thesis:** RAG-based architecture for ISO 27001 + ITGC audit frameworks  \n",
    "**Goal of this notebook:** Install dependencies, load both source documents, and verify the raw data is correctly parsed before any chunking or embedding.\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "## Architecture Overview\n",
    "```\n",
    "[ISO 27001 PDF]  ──►  [PDF Parser]   ──►  ┐\n",
    "                                           ├──► [Chunks + Metadata] ──► [Embeddings] ──► [Vector Store]\n",
    "[ITGC Excel]     ──►  [Excel Parser] ──►  ┘\n",
    "```\n"
   ]
  },
