   "source": [
    "## 1.3 Parse the ITGC Excel File\n",
    "\n",
    "The Excel has 4 sheets, each representing a control domain:\n",
    "- **Access Management** — 7 controls with full Evidence column\n",
    "- **Change Management** — 11 controls (3-column format, no Evidence column)\n",
    "- **Computer Operations** — 8 controls with full Evidence column  \n",
    "- **Program Development** — 11 controls with full Evidence column\n",
    "\n",
    "We load all 4 sheets and normalize them into a unified list of control dictionaries, with `domain` as metadata."
   ]
