    "## 1.4 Parse the ISO 27001 PDF\n",
    "\n",
    "The ISO 27001:2022 document has two logically distinct parts we care about:\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **Main clauses (4–10):** ISMS requirements — each sub-clause becomes a chunk  \n",
    "2. **Annex A:** 93 controls across 4 domains (5=Organizational, 6=People, 7=Physical, 8=Technological)\n",
    "\n",
    "We use `pypdf` to extract the text page by page, then apply clause-aware splitting to preserve the document hierarchy as metadata."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 9,
   "id": "74f51874-573f-4770-bc8a-601974740f85",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
