    "We build a **hybrid index** — two complementary retrieval methods:\n",
    "\n",
    "| Index | Method | Good at |\n",
    "|---|---|---|\n",
    "| FAISS | Dense vector similarity | Semantic meaning, paraphrases |\n",
    "| BM25 | Sparse keyword matching | Exact terms, control IDs, acronyms |\n",
