    "# --- Fix A: ISO-7.5.3 is wrongly tagged Physical / annex_a_control ---\n",
    "# Clause 7.5.3 (Control of documented information) belongs to the ISMS body\n",
    "# It got re-tagged because it contains the word 'Control' in its text\n",
