   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "1a688d38-f1de-42c4-b87c-db90355da63f",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2.4 Build FAISS Index\n",
    "\n",
    "We use `IndexFlatIP` (Inner Product) on L2-normalized vectors — this is equivalent to cosine similarity and gives exact nearest-neighbor search. At 173 documents this is perfectly fast; no need for approximate methods."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 28,
   "id": "bb02c75f-32a6-457e-8fd9-134cef7b6434",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "✅ FAISS index built\n",
      "   Index type    : IndexFlatIP (exact cosine similarity)\n",
      "   Vectors stored: 158\n",
      "   Dimension     : 384\n",
      "\n",
      "Smoke test (self-retrieval of doc 0):\n",
      "  Rank 1: doc_idx=0 | score=1.0000 | ITGC-ACC-01\n",
      "  Rank 2: doc_idx=1 | score=0.8854 | ITGC-ACC-02\n",
      "  Rank 3: doc_idx=6 | score=0.8640 | ITGC-ACC-07\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "import faiss\n",
    "\n",
    "DIM = embeddings.shape[1]   # 384\n",
    "\n",
    "faiss_index = faiss.IndexFlatIP(DIM)\n",
    "faiss_index.add(embeddings.astype(np.float32))\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f'✅ FAISS index built')\n",
    "print(f'   Index type    : IndexFlatIP (exact cosine similarity)')\n",
    "print(f'   Vectors stored: {faiss_index.ntotal}')\n",
    "print(f'   Dimension     : {DIM}')\n",
    "\n",
    "# Quick smoke test — query with the first document's own embedding\n",
    "test_vec = embeddings[0:1].astype(np.float32)\n",
    "scores, indices = faiss_index.search(test_vec, k=3)\n",
    "print(f'\\nSmoke test (self-retrieval of doc 0):')\n",
    "for rank, (idx, score) in enumerate(zip(indices[0], scores[0])):\n",
    "    print(f'  Rank {rank+1}: doc_idx={idx} | score={score:.4f} | {documents[idx][\"control_id\"]}')"
   ]
  },
